-- Hopson to Buy Beijing Industrial-Park Office Project for 6.88 Billion Yuan
-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 2010-11-03T15:11:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-03/hopson-to-buy-beijing-industrial-park-office-project-for-6-88-billion-yuan.html
Hopson Development Holdings Ltd .
agreed to pay 6.88 billion yuan for project company that’s
building 38 loft-style office buildings in a Beijing industrial
park, the company said in a Hong Kong stock exchange filing.  The company will pay 2.31 billion yuan in cash and issue
new shares for the balance of the consideration, according to
today’s statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Joshua Fellman at 
 jfellman@bloomberg.net  